undice.', 'Synergism', 'Fluorouracil, Pemetrexed, Mercaptopurine, Cladribine, Trifluridine, Floxuridine, Gemcitabine, Nelarabine, Cytarabine, Pralatrexate, Fludarabine, More', 'Dabrafenib, Asciminib, Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Avapritinib, Ibrutinib, Tivozanib, Zanubrutinib, Lorlatinib, Ripretinib, Alpelisib, More', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/36854/', '[1] "Product Information. Clolar (clofarabine)." sanofi-aventis, Bridgewater, NJ.', 1767369485);
