r', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/36964/', '[1] Agencia Española de Medicamentos y Productos Sanitarios Healthcare "Centro de información online de medicamentos de la AEMPS - CIMA. Available from: URL: https://cima.aemps.es/cima/publico/home.html." ([2018]):[2] "Product Information. Vyndaqel (tafamidis)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals Group, New York, NY.[3] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[4] "Product Information. Hivid (zalcitabine)." Roche Laboratories, Nutley, NJ.', 1767369485);
